Endpoint	      Method	      Description
/update	        POST	        Upload .bin files for OTA updates.
/stream	        GET	          Real-time debugging console.
/debug	        GET	          Poll-based debug log retrieval.
/list	          GET	          List files in SPIFFS.
/upload	        POST	        Upload a file to SPIFFS.
/download	      GET	          Download a file from SPIFFS.
/delete	        GET	          Delete a file from SPIFFS.
